dmca.title: Medical Equipment Website Claims Infringement by Competitor
dmca.body:
February 28, 2004

Google, Inc.
Attn. Customer Support, DCMA Complaints
[private]
Mountain View, CA 94043

Notice Of Infringement Of Copyrighted Material

1. The copyrighted work is the original text and artwork for several product and product category pages from http://home-med-equip.com. It includes original product photographs, animated images, and text.

2. The material can be viewed in several product categories, for example Bath Safety Products, Scooters, Walkers, Commodes, Recliners, Bed Accessories, Patient Lifts, Etc. all linked from http://home-med-equip.com
